    b19r_visser_death2          "Even through his glasses, I see his eyes instantly dilate. He let's go of me as he starts trashing about with his knife."
    b19r_visser_death3          "I move away keeping between this lunatic and Crystal. He screams, trying to retain control. He lunges forward with all his enhanced might, but misses me and overextends himself."
