    xantech_entrance_desc       "Xantech Cybernetics' ostentatious building rises above us all like a giant middle finger to our hardships."
    xantech_lobby_desc1         "The elevator dings at the 53rd floor, where the Xantech's datacenter is supposed to be."
    xantech_lobby_desc2         "*DING*"
    xantech_lobby_desc3         "Drek. There's a tinman guarding the server room."
    xantech_fail_enter_servers  "The tinman steps in front of us, blocking the entrance."
    xantech_crystal_lax         "Crystal nudges me to give her the coffee and laxative. After mixing them together, she walks to the tinman while I hide around the corner."
    xantech_laxative1           "The tinman takes the coffee from Crystal, eager to make her happy. A few moment pass when we can hear a horrible sound coming from his stomach."
    xantech_laxative2           "In a show of complete dereliction of duty, the tinman abandons his post and runs out of the room as quickly as the coffee is running through him."
    xantech_corridor_desc       "Endless corridors crisscross this floor."
    xantech_medical_desc        "A spotless medical bay. Everything here is state-of-the-art."
    xantech_medicine_closet1    "Medicines of all kinds. Nothing immediately useful."
    xantech_medicine_closet2    "Wait. What's this? KwikyLax?"
    xantech_medicine_closet3    "'World's first military-grade laxative. Declare war on constipation!'"
    xantech_medicine_closet4    "I think we all know where this going."
    xantech_medicine_closet_end "Nothing else of use in here."
    xantech_cafe_desc1          "The breakroom on this floor is a fully stocked cafe. Perhaps working for Xantech wouldn't be the worst thing..."
    xantech_cafe_desc2          "Better not to be seduced by their corporate perks. I had a job to do."
    xantech_coffee_machine      "The coffee from this machine smells real good. I'd better take a cup."
    xantech_has_coffee          "One cup is enough for now. I can always come back."
    xantech_move_to_server      "With the tinman gone, we move into the server room"
    xantech_servers_desc        "The server room has an enormous server rack, clearly all of Xantech's data flowed through here."
    xantech_datablade1          "Using Visser's keycard, I unlock the terminal from the main data blade. I take SegF4ault's data stick and insert it in the expectant port."
    xantech_datablade2          "I wait a few moments, but nothing seems to be happening."
    xantech_datablade3          "*RING RING*"
    xantech_datablade4          "The trap is set. Now we wait."

; Location: XanCon
; ==============================================================================
    xancon_desc1                "For the next day, we lay low."
    xancon_desc2                "It's anyone's guess if Xander is worried about Visser. If he is, he doesn't show it as XanCon is in full swing."
    xancon_desc3                "SegF4ult forges us tickets allowing us to sneak on to the expo floor. We get there just as the Keynote is underway."

    xancon_desc4                "Xander Vane, one of the wealthiest men on the planet."
    xancon_desc5                "Xander Vane, trying to squeeze every single credit from those who have none."
    xancon_desc6                "Like Icarus before him, he's flying too close to the sun and it's time for him to fall."

    xancon_desc7                "The crowd erupts in raucous applause."
    xancon_desc8                "More applause from the crowd."

    xancon_desc9                "The screen behind Xander flickers and the contents is replaced with video clips and audio logs playing in quick succession."
    xancon_desc10               "The crowd begins to roar, confused -- is this a joke?"
    xancon_desc11               "But as horror creeps on Xander's face, they realize this all too real."
    xancon_desc12               "Xander looks into the crowd, and with almost supernatural precision, his eyes lock onto Danni's."
    xancon_desc13               "Like a salmon swimming upstream, Xander pushes his way through the crowd as he makes his way to us in a blinding rage."

    xancon_danni1               "Danni punches him in the face."
    xancon_danni2               "As Xander reels from the hit, she knees him in the groin."
    xancon_danni3               "He double over, she kicks him in the face as he lands on his ass."
    xancon_desc14               "Mid sentence, three men dressed in black, wearing sunglasses and earpieces appear behind Xander."
    xancon_desc15               "Exhibiting a gross misunderstanding of the situation, Xander orders them to arrest us."

    xancon_desc16               "Xander struggles and attempts to make a run for it to no avail."
    xancon_desc17               "Almost bored, the lead man in black jabs Xander with something and he goes limp."
    xancon_desc18               "Just as quickly as they arrived, they left."
    xancon_desc19               "It was now time for us make our exit."

